            55.86002731323242,
            517.4774780273438,
            183.11996459960938
          ],
          "text": "₹ 50/- per piece irrespective of the \ndenomination in addition to the loss. \n \nThe recovery of loss and imposition of \npenalty shall be done immediately on \ndetection, irrespective of number of \npieces. \n \niv. Non-compliance with operational",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            102.54000091552734,
            55.86002731323242,
            302.85723876953125,
            127.43997955322266
          ],
          "text": "iii. Mutilated \nnotes \n(including \ndeliberately cut notes and built-up \nnotes) detected in soiled note \nremittances and currency chest \nbalances",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            304.0199890136719,
            166.73997497558594,
            517.4786376953125,
            279.7200012207031
          ],
          "text": "Penalty of ₹5,000 for each instance of \nirregularity. \n \nPenalty shall be enhanced to ₹10,000 in \ncase of repetition / recurrence of \nirregularity during a financial year. \n \nPenalty shall be levied immediately.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            123.1199951171875,
            180.54002380371094,
            302.8585510253906,
            597.1199951171875
          ],
          "text": "guidelines by currency chests \ndetected by RBI officials e.g. \n \na) Non-functioning of CCTV, non-\ncompliance with rules / guidelines \npertaining to CCTV, recording \npreservation period and related \nissues. \n \nb) Branch cash / documents kept \nin strong room (CC’s vault). \n \nc) Non-utilization of Note Sorting \nMachines (NSMs) for sorting of \nnotes (NSMs not used for sorting \nof high denomination notes, i.e. \nnotes of denomination ₹100 and \nabove, received over the counter \nor not used for sorting notes \nremitted to chest / RBI) \n \nd) \nNon-conduct \nof \nsurprise \nverification of currency chest \nbalances at (i) bimonthly intervals \nby officials unconnected with the \noperations of currency chest and \n(ii) \nsix-monthly \nintervals \nby \nofficials from the Controlling \nOffice.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            245.36990356445312,
            335.3825378417969,
            365.90631103515625,
            455.9189147949219
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
