          "text": "counter to any member of public \ndespite having stock. \n \nb) Refusal by any bank branch to \nexchange soiled notes / refusal \nby any currency chest branch to \nadjudicate mutilated notes \ntendered by any member of \npublic. \n \nc) Denial of facilities / services to \nlinked branches / linked CCs of \nother banks. \n \nd) Non acceptance of lower \ndenomination notes (i.e. \ndenomination of ₹ 50 and below) \ntendered by members of public \nand linked bank branches for \nexchange/deposit. \n \ne) Detection by RBI of mutilated, \nbuilt up, counterfeit notes in re-\nissuable packets prepared by the \ncurrency chest branches.",
          "font_info": {
